para_trans: Government Decision No. VIP 2022 / Q. 270/2022 Simvya (Revenue),
Madam Cama Marg, Martyr Rajguru Chowk,
Bhandardara under Akole, District Ahmednagar Taluka under Water Resources Department.
Various applications have been made to the government for renaming the reservoir as the revolutionary Veer Raghoji Bhangre Reservoir.
have been obtained. Accordingly, the reservoir was named as "Veer Raghoji Bhangre Reservoir of the First Revolution."
A proposal to rename was under the consideration of the government.
The Bhandardara reservoir in Akole, District Ahmednagar taluka is named after the "revolutionary Veer Raghoji."
The decision has been made available on the government website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
